'''罗纳德·杰克·赖特'''（{{lang-en|Ronald Jack Wright}}，{{bd|1953年|4月8日|2021年|2月7日|catIdx=Wright}}）是一位来自[[得克萨斯州|得克萨斯州]]的美国政治人物。他作为[[共和党_(美国)|共和党人]]，担任{{le|德克萨斯州第六国会选区|Texas's 6th congressional district}}的[[美国众议院|美国众议院]]议员。该选区包括[[阿灵顿_(得克萨斯州)|阿灵顿]]整体和[[沃思堡|沃思堡]]东南部，南部还有一片远郊地区。

赖特在阿灵顿{{le|市议会|City council}}任职并担任[[塔兰特县|塔兰特县]]的税务评估员之后，于2018年当选美国众议院议员，并于2020年连任。赖特在2019年6月被诊断出患有[[肺癌|肺癌]]，在2021年1月21日确诊[[COVID-19|COVID-19]]后于2月7日去世。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202102090014.aspx |title = 美首位國會議員染疫身亡 萊特生前積極挺台|website= CNA|date = 2021-02-09 |language = zh-tw|accessdate = 2021-02-11}}</ref><ref name="Jeffers">{{cite web |last1=Jeffers |first1=Gromer Jr.|date=2021-02-08|title=Rep. Ron Wright dies after battle with COVID-19|url=https://www.dallasnews.com/news/politics/2021/02/08/rep-ron-wright-dies-after-battle-with-covid-19/|access-date=2021-02-09|website=Dallas News|language=en}}</ref>

==早年生活和教育==
罗纳德·杰克·赖特<ref>{{cite web | access-date = 2021-02-09 | url = https://www.legistorm.com/person/bio/10470/Ronald_Jack_Wright.html | website = Legistorm | title = Rep. Ron Wright|language=en}}</ref>1953年4月8日出生于[[得克萨斯州|得克萨斯州]][[切罗基县_(德克萨斯州)|切罗基县]]，是佩吉·达琳和乔治·威利斯·赖特的儿子。他于1971年从{{le|阿兹勒独立学区|Azle Independent School District|阿兹勒高中}}毕业<ref name=about>{{cite web|date=2012-12-03|title=About|url=https://wright.house.gov/about|access-date=2021-02-09|website=Representative Ron Wright|language=en}}</ref>，然后在[[德州大学阿灵顿分校|德州大学阿灵顿分校]]就读两年，学习历史、心理学和政治学<ref name=about/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theshorthorn.com/news/uta-alumni-run-for-offices/article_eda5ba20-9a2d-11e6-bc97-270e0942b3a1.html|title=4 UTA alumni run for 3 offices|last=Vera|first=Ariana |website=The Shorthorn|language=en|access-date=2021-02-09}}</ref>。

==职业==
进入政坛之前，赖特曾在陶瓷冷却塔公司（{{lang|en|Ceramic Cooling Tower, Inc}}）工作。他在20世纪90年代为《沃思堡星报》（{{lang|en|Fort Worth Star-Telegram}}）撰写了几篇评论文章，建议公开处决和展示尸体以遏制犯罪。<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-06-30|title=Arlington congressman Ron Wright’s Democratic opponent blasts him for old columns|url=https://www.dallasnews.com/news/politics/2020/06/30/arlington-rep-ron-wright-criticized-by-democratic-opponent-over-controversial-1990s-columns/|access-date=2021-02-09|website=Dallas News|language=en}}</ref>

赖特于2000年至2008年在[[阿灵顿_(得克萨斯州)|阿灵顿]]市议会任职，并于2004年至2008年担任阿灵顿市临时市长<ref>{{cite web|url=https://thehill.com/homenews/campaign/416823-texas-new-members-2019|title=Texas New Members 2019|last=Perks|first=Ashley|date=2018-11-15|website=TheHill|language=en|access-date=2018-12-12}}</ref>。之后赖特于2000年至2009年担任众议员[[乔·巴顿|乔·巴顿]]的地区主任。2009年至2011年，赖特担任巴顿的[[参谋长|幕僚长]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.texastribune.org/2021/02/08/texas-ron-wright-dies/|title=U.S. Rep. Ron Wright dies weeks after testing positive for coronavirus|first=Abby|last=Livingston|date=2021-02-08|language=en|accessdate=2021-02-09|website=The Texas Tribune}}</ref>。同年，赖特被任命为[[塔兰特县|塔兰特县]]税务评估员，任期至2018年结束<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.star-telegram.com/news/local/community/fort-worth/article187665558.html|title=Ron Wright, former Barton chief of staff, runs for Congress | Fort Worth Star-Telegram|last=Mitchell|first=Mitch|date=2017-12-01|publisher=Star-telegram.com|access-date=2021-02-09|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.star-telegram.com/news/politics-government/article187307073.html|title=Joe Barton re-election U.S House nude photos explicit text sexual harassment texas | Fort Worth Star-Telegram|last=Tinsley|first=Anna M.|date=2017-11-30|publisher=Star-telegram.com|language=en|access-date=2021-02-09}}</ref>。

2014年，赖特的办公室在信纸上增加了格言“[[In_God_We_Trust|我们信仰上帝]]”（{{lang|en|In God We Trust}}），包括税务评估信封和税务报表。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2014/aug/8/texas-county-taxman-god-we-trust-stationary-stay/|title=Texas county taxman vows ‘In God We Trust’ stationary will stay|last=Chumley|first=Cheryl K. |website=The Washington Times|language=en|date=2014-08-08|access-date=2021-02-09}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.christiantoday.com/article/texas-county-tax-office-adds-in-god-we-trust-to-stationery/39312.htm|title=Texas county tax office adds 'In God We Trust' to stationery|last=Marie|first=Brownie|date=2014-08-04|website=Christian Today|language=en|access-date=2021-02-09}}</ref>

2018年，赖特的办公室因错误地将{{le|税收留置权|Tax lien}}和账单放在错误的塔兰特县家庭而受到{{le|KDFW|KDFW}}的审查。在接受KDFW的史蒂夫·诺维洛采访时，赖特多次对此案发表错误言论。<ref>{{Citation|title=Tax Collector threatens couple to pay previous home owner's property taxes or lose home|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sUAmRqhQp0A|language=en|access-date=2021-02-09}}</ref>

==美国众议院==
===选举===
{{le|2018年美国众议院选举 (得克萨斯州)#第六选区|2018 United States House of Representatives elections in Texas#District 6|2018年}}，赖特竞选{{le|得克萨斯州第六国会选区|Texas's 6th congressional district}}的[[美国众议院|美国众议院]]议员，接替巴顿，后者与女性分享的露骨照片在网上被曝光后引起全国关注，并宣布不再寻求连任<ref name=foxnews20171122>{{cite news |url=http://www.foxnews.com/politics/2017/11/22/republican-rep-joe-barton-apologizes-after-lewd-photo-text-surfaces.html |title=Republican Rep. Joe Barton apologizes after lewd photo surfaces |work=Fox News|first= Alex |last=Pappas |date=2017-11-22|language=en|accessdate=2021-02-09}}</ref><ref name=politico20171122>{{cite news |url=https://www.politico.com/story/2017/11/22/gop-congressman-barton-apologizes-for-nude-selfie-259442 |title=GOP congressman Barton apologizes for nude selfie |work=Politico |first=Kyle |last=Cheney | date=2017-11-22|accessdate=2021-02-09|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.dallasnews.com/opinion/editorials/2017/11/27/cringe-worthy-photo-let-voters-decide-rep-joe-bartons-future |title=After cringe-worthy photo, let voters decide on Rep. Joe Barton's future |work=The Dallas Morning News |author=Editorial Board |date=2017-11-27|accessdate=2021-02-09|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Leslie |first=Katie |date=2017-11-30 |title= Rep. Joe Barton: I will not seek re-election|url=https://www.dallasnews.com/news/politics/2017/11/30/rep-joe-barton-will-not-seek-re-election |work=Dallas Morning News |location=Dallas, TX |access-date=2021-02-09 |language=en}}</ref>。莱特在初选中获得第一名，但没有达到避免决选所需的50%多数票。他在决选中与{{le|杰克·埃尔泽伊|Jake Ellzey}}对决<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.texastribune.org/2018/04/18/texas-congress-district-2018-election-jake-ellzey-ron-wright/|title=Meet the Texas Republican runoff candidates seeking to replace U.S. Rep. Joe Barton|first=Alana Rocha, Christina Shaman, Justin Dehn and Todd|last=Wiseman|date=2018-04-18|website=The Texas Tribune|language=en|accessdate=2021-02-09}}</ref>，并以52%的得票率获胜<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.weatherforddemocrat.com/news/local_news/now-that-runoffs-are-over-its-off-to-the-november-races/article_545274b8-e3a4-520e-9a4b-180a756c3319.html |title=Now that runoffs are over, it's off to the November races | Local News |publisher=weatherforddemocrat.com |date=2018-05-26 |accessdate=2021-02-09|language=en}}</ref>。在大选中，赖特击败了民主党人{{le|亚娜·桑切斯|Jana Sanchez}}<ref>{{cite web|author=Alana Rocha, Christina Shaman, Justin Dehn and Todd Wiseman |url=https://www.texastribune.org/2018/04/18/texas-congress-district-2018-election-jake-ellzey-ron-wright/ |title=Meet the Texas Republican runoff candidates seeking to replace U.S. Rep. Joe Barton (video) |publisher=The Texas Tribune |date=2018-04-18 |access-date=2021-02-09|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Kennedy |first=Bud |url=https://www.star-telegram.com/opinion/opn-columns-blogs/bud-kennedy/article211703054.html |title=Former Joe Barton aide Ron Wright faces Jana Lynne Sanchez | Fort Worth Star-Telegram |publisher=Star-telegram.com |date=2018-05-23 |access-date=2021-02-09|language=en}}</ref>。

赖特在{{le|2020年美国众议院选举 (得克萨斯州)#第六选区|2020 United States House of Representatives elections in Texas#District 6|2020年}}击败了律师斯蒂芬·丹尼尔，再次当选。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.dallasnews.com/news/elections/2020/11/04/us-rep-ron-wright-of-arlington-defends-his-seat-in-congress-against-texas-democrat-stephen-daniel/|title=U.S. Rep. Ron Wright of Arlington defends his seat in Congress against Texas Democrat Stephen Daniel|date=2020-11-04|website=Dallas News|accessdate=2021-02-09|language=en}}</ref>

===任期===
2019年6月，堕胎权利倡导组织{{lang|en|Reproaction}}发布了一段视频，视频显示，赖特说女性“绝对”应该因为实施自我管理的堕胎而受到惩罚，因为“她们犯下了谋杀罪”。<ref name="Adams">{{cite news |last1=Adams |first1=Matthew |title=Should Women be Punished for Having Abortions? 'Absolutely,' Arlington Rep. Ron Wright Says in Video |url=https://www.nbcdfw.com/news/politics/Should-Women-be-Punished-for-Having-Abortions-Absolutely-Arlington-Rep-Ron-Wright-Says-in-Video-510948501.html |access-date=2021-02-10|language=en |publisher=The Dallas Morning News |date=2019-06-06}}</ref>

2020年12月，赖特是126名签署了一份[[法院之友|法院之友]]摘要的共和党众议员之一，以支持[[德克萨斯州诉宾夕法尼亚州|德克萨斯州诉宾夕法尼亚州]]<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/12/10/politics/read-house-republicans-texas-supreme-court/index.html|title=Brief from 126 Republicans supporting Texas lawsuit in Supreme Court|first=Daniella |last=Diaz|work=CNN|access-date=2021-02-10|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201212000435/https://www.cnn.com/2020/12/10/politics/read-house-republicans-texas-supreme-court/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，这是一项向[[美国最高法院|美国最高法院]]提起的诉讼，对[[2020年美国总统选举|2020年总统选举]]结果——[[乔·拜登|乔·拜登]]击败了现任总统[[唐纳德·特朗普|唐纳德·特朗普]]提出质疑<ref>{{cite web|last=Blood|first=Michael R.|last2=Riccardi|first2=Nicholas|date=2020-12-05|title=Biden officially secures enough electors to become president|url=https://apnews.com/article/election-2020-joe-biden-donald-trump-elections-electoral-college-3e0b852c3cfadf853b08aecbfc3569fa|dead-url=no|access-date=2021-02-10|language=en|website=Associated Press News|archive-date=2020-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208201209/https://apnews.com/article/election-2020-joe-biden-donald-trump-elections-electoral-college-3e0b852c3cfadf853b08aecbfc3569fa}}</ref>。最高法院拒绝审理此案，理由是德克萨斯州缺乏根据[[美国宪法第三条|宪法第三条]]对另一州举行的选举结果提出质疑的资格<ref>{{Cite news|last=Liptak|first=Adam|date=2020-12-11|title=Supreme Court Rejects Texas Suit Seeking to Subvert Election|language=en|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/11/us/politics/supreme-court-election-texas.html|access-date=2021-02-10|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2020-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211234955/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/11/us/politics/supreme-court-election-texas.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{cite web|title=Order in Pending Case|url=https://www.supremecourt.gov/orders/courtorders/121120zr_p860.pdf|date=2020-12-11|publisher=Supreme Court of the United States|language=en|access-date=2021-02-10|archive-date=2020-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211234004/https://www.supremecourt.gov/orders/courtorders/121120zr_p860.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

