==健康与去世==
2019年7月，赖特宣布他被诊断为[[肺癌|肺癌]]<ref>{{cite web |last=Wright |first=Ron |date=2019-07-26 |title=Ron Wright - Facebook |url=https://www.facebook.com/daddadwright/posts/10220372293443805 |dead-url=no |access-date=2021-02-10|language=en |website=Facebook}}</ref>。第二年，他因放射治疗带来一系列并发症，导致住院<ref>{{Cite news |last=Livingston |first=Abby |date=2020-09-14 |title=U.S. Rep. Ron Wright, of Arlington, hospitalized due to complications from cancer treatment |work=Texas Tribune |url=https://www.texastribune.org/2020/09/14/ron-wright-hospitalized-cancer/ |dead-url=no |access-date=2021-02-10|language=en}}</ref>。

2021年1月21日，在{{le|2019冠状病毒病得克萨斯州疫情|COVID-19 pandemic in Texas|得克萨斯州的COVID-19大流行}}期间，赖特宣布他[[COVID-19|COVID-19]]检测呈阳性<ref>{{Cite news |last=Samuels |first=Alex |date=2021-01-21 |title=U.S. Rep. Ron Wright, hospitalized with cancer last year, tests positive for coronavirus |work=Texas Tribune |url=https://www.texastribune.org/2021/01/21/texas-ron-wright-coronavirus/ |dead-url=no |access-date=2021-02-10|language=en}}</ref>。他和妻子在[[达拉斯|达拉斯]]住院两周后，赖特于2月7日去世。赖特是第一位感染该疾病后死亡的[[美国国会|美国国会]]现任议员<ref>{{cite web|last1=Pramuk |first1=Jacob|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2021/02/08/rep-ron-wright-of-texas-dies-of-covid.html |title=Republican Rep. Ron Wright of Texas dies of Covid |work=CNBC |date=2021-02-08 |accessdate=2021-02-10|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Flatley |first1=Daniel |last2=House |first2=Billy |date=2021-02-08 |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2021-02-08/texas-republican-wright-dies-after-battling-cancer-covid |title=Ron Wright Is First Sitting Member of Congress to Die After Positive Covid Test |work=Bloomberg |accessdate=2021-02-10|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Crump |first1=James |date=2021-02-08 |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/us-politics/ron-wright-covid-texas-republican-b1799276.html |title=Ron Wright: Republican congressman dies after contracting Covid |work=The Independent |accessdate=2021-02-10|language=en}}</ref>。[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]]的共和党同僚[[卢克·莱特洛|卢克·莱特洛]]于2020年11月当选，也将在[[第117届美国国会|第117届国会]]任职，他在宣誓就职前5天因该疾病的并发症去世<ref name=pol1>{{Cite web|url=https://www.politico.com/news/2020/12/29/luke-letlow-covid-congress-452218|title=Louisiana congressman-elect dies of Covid|first=Melanie|last=Zanona|website=Politico|date=2020-12-29|accessdate=2021-02-10|language=en}}</ref>。

